#  FILE   : ssh
#
#  PURPOSE: Tests to see that ssh rejects an invalid username
#
#  SETUP: The program `/usr/bin/expect' MUST be installed.
#
#  HISTORY:
#    03/03 Jerone Young (jeroney@us.ibm.com)
#    05/03 Dustin Kirkland (k1rkland@us.ibm.com)
